OL,14,F will be erected on reclaimed marshland
OL,15,F adjacent to the factory assembly lines
OL,17,  CITIZEN ACTION:FReport to the         
OL,18,F Lefortovo marshland with one bag of   
OL,19,F essentials. SABRE SCANS will allocate 
OL,20,F barracks or family hives as required. 
